    <item>
      <title>欧盟通过新一轮电动汽车关税战测试其对抗中国的能力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/eu-tests-its-mettle-to-take-on-china-with-new-ev-tariff-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟对中国动用了其最有力的经济工具之一，对电动汽车征收关税，此举增加了中国采取报复措施以及对国内消费者和企业产生不利影响的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/eu-tests-its-mettle-to-take-on-china-with-new-ev-tariff-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 15:33:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院驳回拜登甲烷排放法规暂停申请</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/epa-s-methane-emission-rules-left-in-place-by-supreme-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院暂时拒绝阻止拜登政府打击油井、油罐和管道等导致全球变暖的甲烷排放。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/epa-s-methane-emission-rules-left-in-place-by-supreme-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 15:26:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业报告和罢工决议为哈里斯经济带来提振</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/jobs-report-strike-resolution-offer-harris-momentum-on-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[招聘人数激增为副总统卡马拉·哈里斯在与唐纳德·特朗普就经济问题的斗争中提供了新的防御，在竞选的最后阶段，两人正在争夺各自的愿景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/jobs-report-strike-resolution-offer-harris-momentum-on-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 15:02:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世贸组织领导人竞选将于下周拉开帷幕，比往常提前</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/wto-leadership-race-kicks-off-next-week-earlier-than-usual</link>
      <description><![CDATA[下一任世界贸易组织领导人的选举过程比平时提前启动，候选人任命将于下周开始，竞选期将于 2 月初结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/wto-leadership-race-kicks-off-next-week-earlier-than-usual</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 14:43:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
