    <item>
      <title>以色列“箭”式导弹防御系统对伊朗发挥了作用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/israel-says-iran-attack-successfully-countered-by-arrow-missile-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据以色列制造商负责人介绍，以色列的箭式导弹拦截系统在周二抵御伊朗的袭击时表现符合预期，尽管在特拉维夫等人口密集地区造成了一些损害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/israel-says-iran-attack-successfully-countered-by-arrow-missile-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 14:18:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
